posts.post_content:
Libas Extra Love collection features our signature designs in comfortable plus sizes.
This 2-piece kurta set includes our purple round neck straight kurta with straight palazzo pants. Crafted in cotton, featuring a notched neckline and detailed with bright floral motifs. Comfortable for daily wear.
Style Note : Accessorize with a smart wristwatch to complete the look.
E X T R A L O V E - represents the Extra love, confidence and belief every woman must posess. Its that extra love for yourself that makes you stand out and be unstoppable. Be Fierce, Bold, Independent, but most importantly, be YOU. #Extralovebylibas
